gip / getip                   Displays your IP address

   Format:
      ;gip                    Displays your IP address

   Notes:
      This command is intended for use with the Chat task. In order to open a
         chat session with someone, you'll need to know their IP address; this
         command displays your own IP address, so that your chat buddies can
         contact you.

   User commands:
      gip / getip
